data.description: Welcome to the community of Winfield Lake. Beyond its inviting porch lies a dining space destined for memorable gatherings. The kitchen offers:granite counters, stainless-steel appliances, and 42-inch cabinets, seamlessly opens into a sun-bathed living area, turning every meal into an event.The expansive owner's suite boasts an ensuite bath equipped with an oversized shower and dual sinks. Spacious guest rooms, abundant closets, dedicated media and game rooms, and a backyard ready for relaxation and fun. Built by the renowned Long Lake Ltd, this community offers lakes, walking trails, clubhouses, tennis courts, pool, playgrounds, and top-rated schools. Minutes away from Fort Bend toll road,Highway 6, Beltway 8, and Highway 90. This ideal location grants swift commutes to the medical center, Rice University, downtown Houston. Offering exceptional value in a rapidly expanding community, this residence stands out not just in stature but in its promise of an unparalleled living experience.
